headline: Intercontinental Exchange Reports June Statistics
summary: ATLANTA & NEW YORK, July 03, 2025--Intercontinental Exchange, Inc. (NYSE:ICE), a leading global provider of technology and data, today reported June 2025 trading volume and related revenue statistics, which can be viewed on the company’s investor relations website at https://ir.theice.com/ir-resources/supplemental-information in the Monthly Statistics Tracking spreadsheet.
